  "keyFeatures": [
    "Incremental Structure-from-Motion (SfM) for ordered and unordered image collections",
    "Global SfM pipeline with rotation averaging and global positioning",
    "Hierarchical SfM for large-scale parallel reconstruction",
    "CUDA-accelerated PatchMatch Multi-View Stereo (MVS) for dense depth estimation",
    "Depth map fusion into dense colored point clouds",
    "Poisson and Delaunay surface meshing with mesh simplification and texturing",
    "SIFT and ALIKED (neural) feature extraction with CPU/GPU support",
    "Multiple feature matching strategies: exhaustive, sequential, vocabulary tree, spatial",
    "Multiple camera distortion models: Pinhole, Radial, OpenCV, Fisheye variants",
    "Rig and frame support for multi-sensor platforms and panoramic cameras",
    "Qt-based graphical user interface with real-time 3D visualization",
    "Python bindings (PyCOLMAP) for scripting and integration",
    "SQLite-based feature and match database",
    "Model utilities: alignment, conversion, merging, splitting, geo-registration"
  ],
